	  to distinguish from retroarch.cfg (which does not sync)
	* retroarch.cfg: Remove redundant audio_latency="32" from mGBA override
	  (global changed to 32 in v2.9; override now matches global)
	* retroarch.cfg: Remove redundant audio="32" from PCSX ReARMed override
	  (same reason)
	* retroarch.cfg: Bump source rev.8 → rev.9
	* README.md: §7 Latency: Preemptive Frames notes now explain
	  relationship with run_ahead_frames
	* README.md: §10 Tier 1 mGBA: Remove redundant audio_latency="32"
	* README.md: §10 Tier 2 PCSX ReARMed: Remove redundant audio_latency="32"
	* README.md: Bump revision 8 → 9
	* Cross-reference verification pass: 28 active keys, 26 checklist
	  items, 12 cores, 10 known issues, all TOC anchors confirmed
	* CHANGELOG: Update for v2.10

